# Code Heavy Benchmark

This document contains 50 code blocks for performance testing.


## Code Block 1

```rust
// Code block 1
fn function_1() {
    let x = 1;
    let y = x * 2;
    println!("Result: {}", y);

    for i in 0..10 {
        println!("Iteration: {}", i);
    }

    match x {
        0 => println!("Zero"),
        _ => println!("Non-zero"),
    }
}
```
